_exptl_crystal_grow.pdbx_details    
;Protein stock was at 20mg/ml in 25mM Mes-Bis Tris, pH 6.4, 75mM LiCl, 0.1M EDTA, 1mM DTT.     
The final concentration of inhibitor in the protein solution was 1mM from a 100mM stock solution of compound dissolved in DMSO.The protein was reacted with inhibitor on ice for 6 hours prior to crystallization.The final concentration of PKI in the protein solution was 2mM from stock 100mM dissolved in water.  The final concentration of MEGA8 in the protein solution was 1.5mM from 225mM stock diluted from 790mM in the Hampton additive kit with water.  Two microliters of protein were added to 0.35 microliters of 10% glycerol in buffer and put in sitting drops over 15% methanol diluted with water at 4C.  Cryo was 100mM MES pH6.4, 100mM LiCl, 25% MeOH, 20% MPD., VAPOR DIFFUSION, SITTING DROP, temperature 294K
;
